para_trans: Primary Health Centre, Adas Ta. About upgradation of 30 beds in Rural Hospital as a special case at Kej, District Beed.
Government Decision No: ProAK-2023 / P.No.321 / Health-4
Read: - Letter No. of the Director, Health Services, Mumbai: By J. No. / Room 3 / T-2 / No. No.2354 / Adas, Vida, Banasarola / Prasasa / 11834/23 Date 17.10.2023.

Introduction: - Primary Health Centre Adas, Ta. Kej, District Beed was under the consideration of the government to upgrade the institute to a rural hospital (30 beds). The following decisions are being taken in this regard:
Primary Health Centre Adas, Ta. Kej, District Beed as a special case of the institution Rural Hospital (30)
Upgradation of beds) is being approved.
The decision is available on the Government of Maharashtra's www.maharashtra.gov.in website.
